 Lovers of the Red Sky 

6
00:00:37,500 --> 00:00:42,200
 The characters and settings of this drama are fictional and unrelated to any historical fact. 

7
00:00:43,660 --> 00:00:49,290
 Once upon a time, there was a time where humans and creatures of the earth 

8
00:00:49,290 --> 00:00:54,960
 lived in harmony with unseen beings. 

9
00:00:54,960 --> 00:00:58,880
 Among them was Sam Shin*, 
(Goddess of childbirth) 

10
00:00:58,880 --> 00:01:01,660
 three gods merged into one body. 

11
00:01:01,660 --> 00:01:06,430
 The first god blessed life. 

12
00:01:06,430 --> 00:01:10,850
 The second god controlled death. 

13
00:01:10,850 --> 00:01:16,490
 The third god maintained the balance between the two. 

14
00:01:16,490 --> 00:01:24,500
 One day, the demonic god of death who thirsted for blood gobbled up the god of balance. 

15
00:01:24,500 --> 00:01:27,040
 Once the balance between life and death was broken, 

16
00:01:27,040 --> 00:01:31,240
 the world fell into terror and chaos. 

17
00:01:31,240 --> 00:01:35,740
 From then on, Ma Wang, the demon king who was severed from the body of Sam Shin, 

18
00:01:35,740 --> 00:01:40,460
 lived within the dark desires of humans. 

19
00:01:40,460 --> 00:01:45,560
 One day, a woman who lost her lover to Ma Wang's rampage 

20
00:01:45,560 --> 00:01:48,980
 created a painting. 

21
00:01:49,000 --> 00:01:54,350
 Sam Shin responded to her prayers and became one with the painting. 

22
00:01:54,350 --> 00:02:00,880
 Ma Wang, who had caused chaos in the world, was sealed in the holy painting. 

23
00:02:00,880 --> 00:02:06,290
 Afterward, the woman disappeared without a trace. 

24
00:02:06,290 --> 00:02:09,790
 Episode 1: Red Sky 

25
00:02:09,790 --> 00:02:12,000
 (Dan Dynasty, the first year of King Seongjo's reign) 

26
00:02:13,130 --> 00:02:18,000
 (The abdicated king Yeongjong was able to conquer the world with the power he acquired when Ma Wang entered his body.) 

27
00:02:18,000 --> 00:02:21,700
 When he became afraid of Ma Wang's increasingly rampant bloodshed, he passed on the throne to his son Seongjo. 

28
00:02:21,700 --> 00:02:26,740
 In order to eliminate Ma Wang, a ritual is held to seal the demon king inside king Yeongjong's portrait. 

29
00:02:33,560 --> 00:02:36,150
Eun Oh, have you heard the news?

30
00:02:36,150 --> 00:02:40,480
I hear this royal portrait will be gifted to the subjects to prevent evil.

31
00:02:40,500 --> 00:02:47,100
Something terrible is to be lifted from the abdicated king's body and sealed into this painting.

32
00:02:47,160 --> 00:02:48,940
Please hear my prayers.

33
00:02:48,940 --> 00:02:52,830
Please help my husband finish the royal portrait without trouble.

34
00:02:52,830 --> 00:02:54,220
Please hear my prayer.

35
00:02:54,220 --> 00:02:57,130
 (Hong Eun Oh's wife) 

36
00:03:11,840 --> 00:03:14,360
That is all. You are excused.

37
00:03:14,360 --> 00:03:16,720
But sir, I am a shaman of the Shamanist Bureau—

38
00:03:16,720 --> 00:03:21,200
The sealing ritual will be carried out by the Taoist Bureau.

39
00:03:22,210 --> 00:03:23,840
Yes, sir.

40
00:03:53,200 --> 00:03:55,140
 (Hong Eun Oh: A royal painter) 

41
00:03:55,140 --> 00:03:59,270
 (Gan Yun Guk: A painter) 
 How can a painting be this powerful?

42
00:03:59,270 --> 00:04:01,610
It is truly remarkable.

43
00:04:02,910 --> 00:04:05,600
Now it truly is...

44
00:04:06,390 --> 00:04:09,460
up to the gods.

45
00:04:16,870 --> 00:04:19,370
My baby...

46
00:04:24,260 --> 00:04:26,500
Buddha!

47
00:04:26,500 --> 00:04:28,140
Gods of heaven and earth!

48
00:04:28,140 --> 00:04:30,110
Sam Shin!

49
00:04:30,110 --> 00:04:31,770
Anyone, please...

50
00:04:31,770 --> 00:04:36,300
Please protect my baby!

51
00:04:41,870 --> 00:04:44,040
Sam Shin!

52
00:04:44,040 --> 00:04:46,970
Please protect my baby!

53
00:04:46,970 --> 00:04:50,570
Please... my baby...

54
00:05:13,410 --> 00:05:17,510
 Cheon Gi... Cheon Gi... 

55
00:05:33,970 --> 00:05:37,890
 (Grandmother Sam Shin: 
 a goddess who blesses a child with life) 

56
00:05:59,740 --> 00:06:05,080
My poor Cheon Gi, what shall we do with you?

57
00:06:25,540 --> 00:06:26,510
 (Mi Su: Royal shaman) 

58
00:06:26,510 --> 00:06:29,200
 (Ha Seong Jin: Head of the Taoist Bureau, which conducts rituals dedicated to the sky and stars
) 

59
00:06:37,000 --> 00:06:39,690
Sir! Sir, what's wrong?

60
00:06:39,690 --> 00:06:42,460
Sir! Sir!

61
00:06:55,180 --> 00:06:56,500
Royal Father...

62
00:06:56,500 --> 00:07:00,060
 (King Seongjo: Fourth king of Dan Dynasty) 
 Is it truly possible

63
00:07:00,060 --> 00:07:02,740
  (King Yeongjong: Third king of Dan Dynasty) 
  to seal Ma Wang into your portrait?

64
00:07:02,740 --> 00:07:06,840
That is the only way to banish that demon from this land.

65
00:07:06,840 --> 00:07:13,200
Today, I will make sure to put an end to the endless bloody war with Ma Wang.

66
00:07:15,730 --> 00:07:17,870
Begin.

67
00:07:26,830 --> 00:07:29,210
Om mani...

68
00:07:31,180 --> 00:07:33,920
Om mani padme hum*. 
  (Sanscrit Buddhist mantra) 

69
00:07:34,940 --> 00:07:37,470
Om mani padme hum!

70
00:09:27,090 --> 00:09:32,710
 (Demon King Ma Wang: a god of death)  
 Who dares wake me from my slumber?

71
00:09:32,710 --> 00:09:35,560
You dare wake me?

72
00:09:35,560 --> 00:09:37,390
Insolent fool!

73
00:09:37,390 --> 00:09:39,230
He is the king of the living land!

74
00:09:39,230 --> 00:09:42,740
Show your respect, demon of the underworld!

75
00:09:44,310 --> 00:09:48,320
Don't look into his eyes! You must never look into his eyes!

76
00:10:00,520 --> 00:10:04,680
King, come closer.

77
00:10:05,830 --> 00:10:08,890
Accept me.

78
00:10:08,890 --> 00:10:13,730
You cannot escape me.

79
00:10:33,010 --> 00:10:37,510
Look, is anyone out there?

80
00:10:41,120 --> 00:10:43,140
 (Hwa Cha: a goblin that lives by absorbing power from paintings) 

81
00:11:24,060 --> 00:11:26,140
Sam Shin!

82
00:11:35,350 --> 00:11:40,580
Sam Shin, how dare you!

83
00:12:16,080 --> 00:12:22,930
From this day forward, you will all suffer from drought and famine!

84
00:12:24,900 --> 00:12:30,710
Your descendants will be lost in darkness!

85
00:12:34,230 --> 00:12:40,540
Your descendants will never paint again!

86
00:13:28,040 --> 00:13:31,520
How dare he blind you?

87
00:13:31,520 --> 00:13:38,620
Ma Wang, that demon is truly unchanging and cruel.

88
00:13:38,620 --> 00:13:44,030
Dear child, I cannot undo the curse...

89
00:13:44,030 --> 00:13:50,950
but I shall bless you with a destined partner who can help you avoid the curse.

90
00:14:01,710 --> 00:14:04,360
My Lady, it's a boy!
 (Ha Seong Jin's house in Yangju) 

91
00:14:04,400 --> 00:14:07,900
Sweet baby, your name is Ram.

92
00:14:07,910 --> 00:14:09,070
 Ha Ram: Ha Seong Jin's son 

93
00:14:09,070 --> 00:14:12,080
The eldest son of the noble household of Ha.

94
00:14:12,080 --> 00:14:15,690
- Ha Ram.
- What a beautiful name!

95
00:14:39,450 --> 00:14:40,710
What is the matter?

96
00:14:40,710 --> 00:14:45,110
Will this truly bring peace to the world?

97
00:14:45,110 --> 00:14:48,280
I am afraid the seal will be broken.

98
00:14:48,280 --> 00:14:50,000
Do not fear any longer.

99
00:14:50,000 --> 00:14:53,270
Your reign will be filled with peace and prosperity.

100
00:14:53,270 --> 00:14:55,720
The curse troubles me.

101
00:14:55,720 --> 00:14:59,480
The drought and famine.

102
00:15:16,760 --> 00:15:18,430
What is the meaning of this?

103
00:15:18,430 --> 00:15:20,720
You will not get away with this!

104
00:15:20,720 --> 00:15:21,800
Once the abdicated king finds out—

105
00:15:21,800 --> 00:15:24,140
The abdicated king has chosen the Shamanist Bureau.

106
00:15:24,140 --> 00:15:28,240
It is time for Your Excellency to step down.

107
00:15:28,240 --> 00:15:29,950
Strike him!

108
00:15:32,170 --> 00:15:34,490
Everyone, scatter!

109
00:15:37,120 --> 00:15:39,830
 Death awaits the hunting dog once the hunt is over. 

110
00:15:55,640 --> 00:15:59,670
I only did what I had to do to safeguard the royal family

111
00:15:59,670 --> 00:16:02,900
and the people of this country!

112
00:16:21,000 --> 00:16:24,570
 Nine years later, the ninth year of King Seongjo's reign 

113
00:16:24,570 --> 00:16:26,500
 The sealing ceremony was successful, 

114
00:16:26,500 --> 00:16:28,880
 but the Dan dynasty suffers from drought and famine for nine years because of Ma Wang's curse 

115
00:16:28,880 --> 00:16:31,270
 So the Royal Shaman, Mi Su, searches for a seokcheokdongja to sacrifice during the rain ritual... 

116
00:16:32,670 --> 00:16:34,300
What does that say?

117
00:16:34,300 --> 00:16:37,020
 Divide the crop into ten grades and pay taxes based on how much you salvage  
 I don't know. I can't read.

118
00:16:37,020 --> 00:16:38,390
What do you mean he is not virtuous?

119
00:16:38,390 --> 00:16:41,020
- The king should take charge and...
 - How dare you?

120
00:16:41,020 --> 00:16:42,790
That is why it doesn't rain!

121
00:16:42,790 --> 00:16:46,610
- Do you know how many years it has been?
 - Clear the path!

122
00:16:51,170 --> 00:16:53,970
Make certain not a single grain of rice is taken out!

123
00:16:53,970 --> 00:16:57,320
- Do you understand?
 - Yes, My Lord!

124
00:17:07,140 --> 00:17:10,020
That boy has extraordinary powers!

125
00:17:10,020 --> 00:17:11,930
- It's right here.
 - You are certain this is where the water is?

126
00:17:11,930 --> 00:17:15,110
Come on, let's dig!

127
00:17:15,110 --> 00:17:17,940
He said there is water! We must dig!

128
00:17:20,050 --> 00:17:24,170
Water! It's water!

129
00:17:25,790 --> 00:17:31,570
That child is truly blessed with the divine power of water.

130
00:17:40,370 --> 00:17:42,820
- Father! 
 - Yes.

131
00:17:42,820 --> 00:17:46,460
Ram! You are back.

132
00:17:46,460 --> 00:17:47,900
 - That man... 
 - Yes, Father.

133
00:17:47,900 --> 00:17:51,500
 - is His Lordship Ha Seong Jin. 
 - Come inside. Come.

134
00:17:52,260 --> 00:17:54,310
 So he was alive. 

135
00:17:59,450 --> 00:18:02,050
It has been too long, Sir.

136
00:18:02,050 --> 00:18:04,330
What business have you here?

137
00:18:04,330 --> 00:18:10,130
I realize sorrow and resentment still haunt you after all these years.

138
00:18:10,130 --> 00:18:12,010
You should watch your mouth.

139
00:18:12,010 --> 00:18:14,070
I only followed the abdicated king's orders back then.

140
00:18:14,070 --> 00:18:17,050
Before I put an end to your life right this minute,

141
00:18:17,050 --> 00:18:19,330
tell me your reason for coming to my house.

142
00:18:19,330 --> 00:18:22,070
I am here to summon your son.

143
00:18:25,730 --> 00:18:27,460
You sick wench.

144
00:18:27,460 --> 00:18:31,610
I'm sure you are not ignorant of the fact that your son was born with the divine power of water.

145
00:18:31,610 --> 00:18:34,770
- I will pretend I did not hear you.
 - Lord!

146
00:18:34,770 --> 00:18:38,620
This country has suffered from drought for the past nine years.

147
00:18:38,620 --> 00:18:40,600
We need your son for this year's Seokcheok* rain ritual.
  (ritual using a lizard) 

148
00:18:40,600 --> 00:18:41,990
How dare you!

149
00:18:41,990 --> 00:18:45,970
Shut your mouth and leave!

150
00:19:04,310 --> 00:19:06,810
Your divine powers have grown stronger.

151
00:19:06,810 --> 00:19:09,610
I am now the head royal shaman of the Shamanist Bureau. 
  (The head shaman is the one who conducts national rites)  

152
00:19:10,620 --> 00:19:14,530
I will take your son for the ritual as the seokcheokdongja*.
  (=“lizard boy”. A child to lead the lizard  rain ritual)  

153
00:19:14,530 --> 00:19:16,760
You do not have a choice in this matter.

154
00:19:16,760 --> 00:19:19,110
Make your preparations.

155
00:19:19,110 --> 00:19:22,810
I shall leave with your son tomorrow as soon as dawn breaks.

156
00:19:23,880 --> 00:19:27,190
 (Gwanyang: The capital city of Dan dynasty) 

157
00:19:28,220 --> 00:19:32,680
What is the most important part of a portrait?

158
00:19:32,680 --> 00:19:33,600
 (Hong Cheon Gi) 

159
00:19:33,600 --> 00:19:36,600
It is not my eyes that look upon it.

160
00:19:36,610 --> 00:19:39,660
It is the eyes that look upon me.

161
00:19:42,530 --> 00:19:44,630
There's the maniac and the eye demon.

162
00:19:44,630 --> 00:19:48,490
My mom says their house is haunted.

163
00:19:48,490 --> 00:19:50,110
Ghosts? Really?

164
00:19:50,110 --> 00:19:52,240
Do you really believe that?

165
00:19:52,240 --> 00:19:56,530
Ghosts don't exist. Look carefully.

166
00:19:58,030 --> 00:20:01,210
Come and get it! Come and get it!

167
00:20:01,210 --> 00:20:04,480
- Come and get it!
 - Give that back! That's my father's painting!

168
00:20:04,480 --> 00:20:06,940
- Come and get it!
 - Give it back!

169
00:20:08,500 --> 00:20:10,840
Dirty rat!

170
00:20:10,840 --> 00:20:12,570
Dirty rat.

171
00:20:12,570 --> 00:20:15,150
Disgusting. Scram!

172
00:20:16,760 --> 00:20:19,610
Don't mess with my daughter Cheon Gi!

173
00:20:19,610 --> 00:20:21,740
- Don't touch Cheon Gi!
 - What's wrong?

174
00:20:21,740 --> 00:20:25,240
Father, stop! Father, I'm all right! Father!

175
00:20:25,240 --> 00:20:28,270
Father, please! I'm all right.

176
00:20:28,270 --> 00:20:30,130
Father!

177
00:20:30,130 --> 00:20:32,340
Let's go! Come on!

178
00:20:32,340 --> 00:20:33,670
Run!

179
00:20:33,670 --> 00:20:36,430
- Let's go!
 - Hurry, run!

180
00:20:36,430 --> 00:20:38,550
Make way!

181
00:20:39,690 --> 00:20:41,990
Make way!

182
00:20:49,280 --> 00:20:51,860
Don't look into his eyes.

183
00:20:51,860 --> 00:20:54,460
- We must not look into the eyes.
 - Father?

184
00:20:54,460 --> 00:20:58,000
Don't look into his eyes.

185
00:20:58,000 --> 00:20:59,860
Don't look into his eyes!

186
00:20:59,860 --> 00:21:02,090
 I sense demon energy. 

187
00:21:02,090 --> 00:21:05,750
- Must not look into the eyes...
 - Father...

188
00:21:15,670 --> 00:21:17,270
Stop!

189
00:21:17,270 --> 00:21:19,080
Please stop!

190
00:21:19,080 --> 00:21:20,440
 What is this energy? 

191
00:21:20,500 --> 00:21:25,000
My father is not mentally well.

192
00:21:25,660 --> 00:21:27,190
Where am I?

193
00:21:27,190 --> 00:21:30,130
Father. Father.

194
00:21:32,390 --> 00:21:34,620
- Cheon Gi...
 - Father.

195
00:21:34,620 --> 00:21:37,170
Do you recognize me?

196
00:21:38,680 --> 00:21:41,350
- Cheon Gi!
 - Father.

197
00:21:41,350 --> 00:21:44,170
My Cheon Gi!

198
00:21:46,920 --> 00:21:48,490
Eun Oh!

199
00:21:48,490 --> 00:21:50,360
H-Hong Eun Oh!

200
00:21:51,500 --> 00:21:53,800
Is... Is it really you?

201
00:21:54,570 --> 00:21:56,320
It is you...

202
00:21:57,350 --> 00:21:59,330
You were alive!

203
00:21:59,330 --> 00:22:01,130
Sir Ha Seong Jin!

204
00:22:01,130 --> 00:22:03,600
It is so good to see you again.

205
00:22:03,600 --> 00:22:05,890
 Shamanist Bureau: 
managed shamans and conducted rituals for the royal family 

206
00:22:05,890 --> 00:22:08,940
Are you all right?

207
00:22:08,940 --> 00:22:11,140
Your manic attack earlier seemed quite severe.

208
00:22:11,140 --> 00:22:13,190
The seizures began after that day

209
00:22:13,190 --> 00:22:16,340
and ever since, my memories gradually slip away.

210
00:22:16,340 --> 00:22:22,230
I am worried to death for my little Cheon Gi because of my illness.

211
00:22:22,230 --> 00:22:26,360
She was born that day in the year of the ox.

212
00:22:29,290 --> 00:22:32,720
My son was also born on the same day.

213
00:22:32,720 --> 00:22:35,470
Was your son not affected?

214
00:22:37,750 --> 00:22:40,720
Ha Ram, go play in the yard.

215
00:22:40,720 --> 00:22:44,580
- Yes, Father.
 - Cheon Gi, go with him.

216
00:22:44,580 --> 00:22:48,240
Then may I go to the Baegyu   (White Elm)    Painting Institute?

217
00:22:48,240 --> 00:22:52,050
- Father, please.
 - What a bright child.

218
00:22:52,050 --> 00:22:54,670
Ha Ram, why don't you go with her?

219
00:22:54,670 --> 00:22:56,550
Yes, Father.

220
00:23:04,270 --> 00:23:06,490
It is a path I know well.

221
00:23:06,490 --> 00:23:08,970
I am not following you.

222
00:23:08,970 --> 00:23:11,500
You don't own this land.

223
00:23:21,860 --> 00:23:24,290
 Baegyu Painting Institute 

224
00:23:26,070 --> 00:23:28,160
- Where is this?
 - Goodness!

225
00:23:28,160 --> 00:23:30,000
You've followed me, after all.

226
00:23:30,000 --> 00:23:32,670
I was walking ahead of you.

227
00:23:32,670 --> 00:23:35,480
Was that supposed to be a joke?

228
00:23:36,610 --> 00:23:38,230
Where is this?

229
00:23:38,230 --> 00:23:40,800
This is the Baegyu Painting Institute.

230
00:23:40,800 --> 00:23:44,940
- It is a painters' institution. 
 - Painters' institution?

231
00:23:44,940 --> 00:23:48,390
They make paintings and sell them.

232
00:23:49,640 --> 00:23:54,250
 Transfer Simulation: imitation technique  
 The painting for today's replication lesson is not an old one.

